list.name: Default
list.comment: * Project name changed to Droidefense for better search on google, github etc * Project external configuration file changed from config.properties to config.json * Profiling mode added as CLI option for third party profiler tools

task.summary: * Infinite recursion problem solved on analyzers
* There is some kind of bug when trying to generate json from apkrproject object. Stackoverflow given
* Added velocity engine dependency * Added velocity config test
* Added API method category to string classifier * Added static report template generation features. Still needs to be coded using Apache Velocity engine syntax.
* Modularized core dependencies in different packages for easier maintenance. * Added a new report template. * Changed graph node generation method

* Project structure reorganized * flow and om packages are being externalized for a better modular design. Will be added on second release. * Added Virtual file system lib for speeding up scan process and avoid not needed IO operations on HDD. This lib is still an alpha version that needs to be optimized for high performance using Java NIO, concurrency support, etc.
